l; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Please input details for an alternative referee that meets all of the above criteria on the <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/Login.aspx">Staffing Website. </a></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"><br></span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">If you feel the reference you provided is suitable and in line with the above conditions then please re-submit this referee, choose the relationship 'other' and fully detail why they are appropriate, the nature of your relationship and the information about contact details.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">If we are encountering problems with both of your references, you will receive another email detailing that specific issue.</p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">All or some of the references section has been unlocked for you to make changes to your referee(s) details.</p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">For further assistance with your references section please <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/contact/">contact your local staffing team</a>, quoting the email reference number below in any correspondence.</p>]]></td>
